    Right click to reset
    Hold Ctrl to select</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="pianoroll.tool.pitchline">Pitch Line Tool (Shift + 1)
    Left click to draw straight line
    Right click to reset
    Hold Ctrl to select</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="pianoroll.tool.pitchscurve">Pitch S-Curve Tool (Shift + 2)
